abstract: YouTube and Lenovo announce SpaceLab contest aimed at students ages 14 to 18 who will make videos proposing experiments that could be conducted at International Space Station.
snippet: YouTube and Lenovo, the computer manufacturer, announced a science contest called SpaceLab for students around the world ages 14 to 18.
lead_paragraph: YouTube and Lenovo, the computer manufacturer, announced a science contest called SpaceLab for students around the world ages 14 to 18.
